            <title>[LU-6107] Interop 2.6.0&lt;-&gt;2.7 sanityn test_82: FAIL: multiop 1 </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6107</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/ebd13b0c-9624-11e4-acfc-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/ebd13b0c-9624-11e4-acfc-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_82 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;multiop 1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanityn test 82: fsetxattr and fgetxattr on orphan files == 23:28:25 (1420529305)
multiop /mnt/lustre/f82.sanityn vO_ac
TMPPIPE=/tmp/multiop_open_wait_pipe.2294
multiop /mnt/lustre2/f82.sanityn vo_Ac
TMPPIPE=/tmp/multiop_open_wait_pipe.2294
fgetxattr: No such file or directory
 sanityn test_82: @@@@@@ FAIL: multiop 1 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
